          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Must Attach to" typeId="2c63-5e3f-9132-459d">This unit must attach to either:
a) LIGHT TROUPE
b) DARK TROUPE
c) TWILIGHT TROUPE</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="Immaculate Choreography" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="71d5-b598-ee4e-1c0d">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After this unit&apos;s Move step, you may select another TROUPE unit visible to this unit, and select ‘Perform’, ‘Accompany’, or ‘Await  Cue’ from below.


Perform: This unit gains the following ability until the End step: 


      Blooming Carnage: For each attack made for this unit, reroll a Hit Roll of 1 for that attack.


Accompany: The selected unit becomes ready, then skip this turn’s  Attacks step.


Await Cue: This unit becomes ready, then skip this turn’s Attacks step.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
